\c 20
\s Maguta matanhatu eutiziro
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Joshua achiti:
\v 2 Taura kuvana vaIsraeri uti: Zvimisirei maguta eutiziro andakareva kwamuri neruoko rwaMozisi.
\v 3 Kuti muurayi anouraya munhu asiri maune asingazivi atizireko. Zvino achava kwamuri utiziro pamutsivi weropa.
\v 4 Kana achitizira kune rimwe remaguta ayo, achamira pamukova wesuwo reguta, uye achareva nyaya yake munzeve dzevakuru veguta iro; zvino vachamugamuchira kwavari muguta ndokumupa nzvimbo kuti agare pakati pavo.
\v 5 Zvino kana mutsivi weropa akamudzingirira, havangapi muurayi muruoko rwake, nokuti wakarova wekwake asingazivi, asina kumuvenga zuro \add na\add*marimwezuro.
\v 6 Zvino achagara muguta iro kusvika amira pamberi peungano kutongwa, kusvika pakufa kwemupristi mukuru achavapo mazuva iwayo; ipapo muurayi achadzoka auye kuguta rake nekuimba yake, kuguta kwaakatiza achibva.
\p
\v 7 Zvino vakanatsa Kedheshi muGarirea panyika yezvikomo yaNafutari, neShekemu panyika yezvikomo yaEfuremu, neKiriyati-Aribha rinova Hebhuroni panyika yezvikomo yaJudha.
\v 8 Nemhiri kwaJoridhani paJeriko kumabvazuva vakapa Bhezeri murenje pabani kubva kurudzi rwaRubheni, neRamoti muGiriyadhi kubva kurudzi rwaGadhi, neGorani muBhashani kubva kurudzi rwaManase.
\v 9 Awa aiva maguta akamisirwa vana vose vaIsraeri nemutorwa agere pakati pavo semweni, kuti ani nani anouraya munhu asiri maune atizireko, kuti arege kufa neruoko rwemutsivi weropa, kusvika amira pamberi peungano.